headline: Does Parker Hannifin’s 41% 2025 Surge Still Make Sense Given Growth Expectations?
summary: If you are wondering whether Parker Hannifin still makes sense at its current price after its massive run, or if you may be late to the party, this breakdown will help you consider whether the current price makes long term sense. The stock has barely paused this year, climbing 40.8% year to date and 38.6% over the last 12 months, on top of an increase of 215.9% over three years and 254.0% over five years.
